subtitleNullable: A dataset containing images of Polish traffic signs
descriptionNullable:
A dataset containing images of Polish traffic signs.

The classification folder contains cut-out images sorted by the traffic sign. The dataset consists of 20 traffic sign types + a single class for all other traffic signs. The classes are:
A1, A2, A7, A17, A21, A30, B1, B2, B20, B21, B22, B23, B33, B36, B41, C2, C4, C12, D1, D6, other
(according to [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Road_signs_in_Poland](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Road_signs_in_Poland))

The detection folder contains full images with aspect ratio of 4:3 along with labels describing the location of the traffic sign on the image in YOLO format.
